data.description: Discover this stunning townhouse located in Snellville.  On the second floor, you will find three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, stylish backsplashes, and modern stainless steel appliances, creating an inviting space. With an open concept floor plan, the townhouse provides a seamless flow between rooms, enhancing the overall sense of spaciousness. Conveniently located right off Highway 78, this property offers easy access to transportation routes, and it is only a short 15-minute drive away from Stone Mountain. Additionally, the townhouse comes with the added convenience of a washer, dryer, and warm inviting foyer with for a comfortable and modern lifestyle.
